Subject: [PATCH] iio: adc: hx711: Fix buffer alignment in iio_push_to_buffers_with_timestamp()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: afe2a789fbf7acd1a05407fc7839cc08d23825e3
